quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  62,9,Ya eyyuhelleziyne amenu iza nudiye lissalati min yevmilcumuÂṀati fesÂṀav ila zikrillahi ve zerulbeyÂṀa zalikum hayrun lekum in kuntum taÂṀlemune
  62,10,Feiza kudÄḟyetissalatu fenteÅiru fiylÂṀardÄḟ vebteÄu min fadlillahi vezkurullahe kesiyren leÂṀallekum tuflihune
  62,11,Ve iza reev ticareten ev lehveninfaddu ileyha ve terekuke kaimen kul ma ÂṀÄḟndallahi hayrun millehvi ve minetticareti vallahu hayrurrazikÄḟyne
  63,1,ÄḞza caekelmunafikune kalu neÅhedu inneke leresulullahi vallahu yaÂṀlemu inneke leresulullahi vallahu yeÅhedu innelmunafikÄḟyne lekazibune
  63,2,ÄḞttehazu eymanehum cunneten fesaddu ÂṀansebiylillahi innehum sae ma kanu yaÂṀmelune
  63,3,Zalike biennehum amenu summe keferu fetubiÂṀa ÂṀala kulubihim fehum la yefkahune
  63,4,Ve iza reeytehum tuÂṀcibuke ecsamuhum ve in yekulu tesmaÂṀ likavlihim keennehum huÅubun musennedetun yahsebune kulle sayhatin ÂṀaleyhim humulÂṀaduvvu fahzerhum katelehumullahu enna yuÂṀfekune